Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.45,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A racing second hand, a returning satellite!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.79,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:11.29,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the lively Detective Boys again!\NThis year's Conan is a little different!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:12.76,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.63,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.85,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
