Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:45.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If my opponent goes for my upper body,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:52.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'll smash 'em with a mid-section to upper body kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:02:00.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ran's always tense on days she has karate matches...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:09.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! You better come cheer me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:12.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'll come right after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:17.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You better! I absolutely can't lose to my opponent today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:19.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you better come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:37.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ran's really raring to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:48.08,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh, it's just construction...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:51.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:55.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry, so I'm off! 4:00, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I gotta hurry to the karate arena
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}or else I'll meet that roundhouse again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Just the voice I don't wanna hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:15.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Crap! I got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:19.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check this out! It's a wideband reversy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:24.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}! It's called a wideband receiver!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Same difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it do, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a powerful radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:35.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can even pick up taxi and cordless phone conversations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a toy to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:41.67,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Send a fire truck immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:45.17,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Rairaiken? I'd like three ramens and two dumplings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, isn't it wrong to listen in\Non people's phone conversations?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's called "wiretapping"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:57.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't bother anybody if we're just listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's pretty creepy, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:03.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Whoops, I'm in trouble if\NI don't go see Ran's match...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:07.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's listen in on Amie Namuro, that singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:12.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? She lives in this area?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:13.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:21.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This receiver only picks up random signals within a 1 kilometer radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Random? That's no fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:27.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can't choose who to listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:31.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch. You turn the dial like so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:35.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until you find someone talking, like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:36.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See! I found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.65,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I have your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:46.74,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I said, I've kidnapped your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:50.27,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Call the cops and she's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:53.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A threatening phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:56.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This for reals?! Where are they talking from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This only listens, so I can't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He kidnapped his daughter! Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it really is a kidnapping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was real kidnapping,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:19.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,all we know is that they're within a 1 kilometer radius!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just 1 kilometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He might call again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:26.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait and see! Okay, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:35.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Detective Boys are back in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:38.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:41.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1750,0)\a6}"Beika Martial Arts Arena"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:41.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1750,0)\a10}"Gyokushinkai Karate Tournament"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Beika Martial Arts Arena"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:48.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Gyokushinkai Karate Tournament"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.93,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}In blue, Ran Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ossu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:01.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Not good. At this rate,\NI'll get stuck with them, again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:06.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.92,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Looks like you haven't called the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:11.98,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:13.19,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Junko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:17.66,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What are you going to do to her?!\NI'll do anything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:19.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:25.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, take your cordless phone and step out onto the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.94,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Good. Now stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.74,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Your satellite dish is in the way! Take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:33.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.21,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Just do what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he making him do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper is watching him from somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:45.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably told him to go onto the balcony to see him better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:52.36,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'd forget about calling the cops if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:55.73,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can see you nice and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:07:01.57,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Do anything funny and I'll kill your daughter on the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:06.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?! Shouldn't we tell the police—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:10.04,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Alright! I'll do whatever you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:15.32,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What is it you want?! Money?!\NDo you want money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:23.99,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't get worked up. Just wait there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He hung up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:37.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But would they believe us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:42.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! All we know is that a Junko-{\i1}chan{\i0} might've been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, they hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:50.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to go to the police and sit around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:55.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll catch the kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But how? We don't have any clues...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned something from that last call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:08.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you getting your math notebook out for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:13.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dr. Agasa's Electronic Map Notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:17.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That inventor relative of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:21.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Here's our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:26.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That receiver picks up signals within a 1 kilometer radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:31.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim's home is somewhere in this circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:34.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, that faint sound in the background...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:40.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a train. The victim probably lives along a train line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:43.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one railway that goes through this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Beika Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:53.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! To the Beika Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it to the train tracks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:07.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the only tracks within the receiver's range!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:12.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the victim is along this 600-meter length of track!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:15.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! It's only 600 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:20.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, isn't there any other way, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one more hint, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:30.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper told him to take down his satellite dish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:31.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:35.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite dishes are pointed to the southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:39.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the victim has a balcony facing southwest, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Then the victim's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has a balcony on the south or west!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:52.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:55.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No question about it! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's tons of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on the opposite buildings, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we don't have enough clues yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:13.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper called back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:20.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Now give us some sort of hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:23.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a clue this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:28.18,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Seems you haven't contacted the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.44,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Is Junko all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.82,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That all depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.22,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You mentioned you'd do anything I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.53,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So first, I want you to get naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:41.36,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:44.09,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Naked! Take your clothes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:49.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! He's making him go to a public bath nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:56.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Some high school girls are about to pass below your apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wave to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:02.07,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Or, do you not care what happens to your daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:08.45,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shout, "Hello!" and wave to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:14.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:16.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:18.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:27.57,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}How's it feel to be made fun of\Nby high school girls in sailor uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:30.91,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Keep doing that for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Sailor uniforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:39.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear quite a few high school girls over the wideband receiver...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:44.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That apartment building is likely on the way to a girls' school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only girls' schools in that 600 meter area
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:50.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,are Seijun Girls' Academy and Beika Girls' High School...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:54.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet high school girls always made fun of the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a girls' school teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:59.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No teacher would do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:03.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out the schools, but I don't know their uniforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:06.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seijun uses blazers. Beika uses sailor uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:13.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to dream about wearing a sailor outfit when I get to high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:19.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but lately I've been considering a blazer and loose socks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think is better?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:23.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A blazer would look better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A sailor outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:33.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Beika Girls' High School!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:36.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That narrows it down to a 300 meter radius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A man waving from his balcony?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:50.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should ask some high school girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:52.09,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:56.89,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You can quit waving now. Now, sing a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:13:01.66,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Sing loud enough for the whole neighborhood to hear! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:10.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must not be this neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some kind of sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:18.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a temple bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The victim lives behind a temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:26.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a taiko drum!\NThe kidnapper must be playing along!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No! That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It sounded just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pile driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pile driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:48.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! The machines that pound piles in at construction sites!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, finding construction sites around here would—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:53.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:09.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow that, it'll lead us to a construction site!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:20.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This narrows it down to a 150 meter radius!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:28.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As close as we are now,\Nit's still a 150 meter radius!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:30.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Without anything definitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.36,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Parents sure are pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:39.03,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}They'll do anything for their kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:43.14,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I know how it feels. I used to be a parent myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}"Used to be"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:48.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The little girl who fell to her death one year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:53.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you remember, as it was from your apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:58.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my daughter who died!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\t(500,750,\c&HCCCCDD&)}"Young Girl Falls to Death"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:04.12,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Tomidokoro-{\i1}san{\i0}?! Is this Tomidokoro-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:08.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm the one whose daughter you murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:15.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! The door to your roof was always off-limits and locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:19.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why was it unlocked then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:23.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone had picked it, or it just broke by chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:27.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One whole week earlier! So why didn't you do anything about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:30.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured nobody ever went up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:34.19,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So it was nobody's fault?! Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:38.66,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm gonna let you experience the same sadness I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.39,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The exact same sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.60,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What're you gonna do to Junko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:45.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:53.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid train crossing! Now we can't hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}One... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Three... Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Five... Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Seven... Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There it is! 8.2 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:27.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know they're this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:32.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It took 8.2 seconds after it passed until I heard it on the receiver!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:39.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(96,96)\fscx110\fs32}Beika Line
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:39.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(378,314)\c&H00&\b0\bord0\shad0\fscx100\fs20}Speed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:39.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,400)\c&H00&\b0\bord0\shad0\fscx100\fs20}1 Second
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:50.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,210)\blur5\a3\bord6\shad0\fs20\c&H446644&\3c&H446644&}Seconds
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.17,0:16:50.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,214)\a3\bord0\shad0\fs20\c&H00&}Seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(440,360)\bord0\shad0\fs24\c&H00&}Victim's Home
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Trains on the Beika Line go 100 km/h!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about 27.8 meters per second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:45.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the train on the receiver\N8.2 seconds after it passed the crossing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:51.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the victim's house\Nis 27.8 meters x 8.2 seconds away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:58.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A building around here with balconies facing south or west!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:02.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And an apartment with a naked man on the balcony...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:08.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the man whose daughter was kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That just leaves the kidnapper's location...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:14.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Damn it! Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:21.06,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'll do anything you say! Just spare my daughter's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.10,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:23.96,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.93,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Good! I was waiting to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get a knife from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A knife?! Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:38.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Now I see! The kidnapper's going to force him to kill himself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}to get revenge without dirtying his own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.61,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:46.39,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Alright. This will be my last demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:51.29,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Thrust the knife into your throat\Nand I'll let your daughter go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:54.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.79,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:59.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you don't care what happens to your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Damn it! If I don't hurry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Where's the kidnapper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.84,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Alright... I'll do what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:14.68,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Just let me talk to Junko one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.91,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:17.19,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:19.35,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Junko! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.72,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Just hold on a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.02,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Daddy! I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:27.33,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I hate this smell! It smells like rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Rubber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The tire factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't see the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:44.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's not the tire factory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:48.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What buildings near the factory have a view of the victim's balcony?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:51.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There's three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:54.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Which one?! Which apartment building?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:02.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The only one downwind from it... is that building!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's gotta be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Somewhere in that building are the kidnapper and Junko-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:12.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan! Do something, quick!\NHe's really gonna kill himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:15.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Junko-{\i1}chan{\i0} is in danger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:19.51,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm gonna let you experience the same sadness I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.35,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The exact same sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The exact same sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper is on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:29.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:31.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of that apartment building!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:34.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of you two call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:35.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.57,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's it! Jab it right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:44.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't be rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Just thrust it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:49.23,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Do it! Thrust it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:52.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Junko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:57.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you hesitating for?! Do it! Jab it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:00.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Junko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:01.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:04.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa! A detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:12.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:21.60,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Junko... forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Junko-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s dad! She's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.22,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I caught the kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.19,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Daddy! I'm safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was rescued!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.15,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Junko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:38.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:43.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you beat him up yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:58.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh, he was so surprised when I showed up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that he fell and hit his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:04.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.41,0:22:41.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:43.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:45.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that means good riddance to these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:51.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, at least it was useful before it broke, Mitsuhiko-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:52.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:54.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:57.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Crap! I forgot!
