Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:02.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:04.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's over already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:09.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that was one mean roundhouse that high school girl won with!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:14.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You mean Ran Mouri?! She was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:17.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So, the clincher was Ran's special roundhouse kick?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:21.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you watch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:27.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Your roundhouse in the finals was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:30.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I used my roundhouse to win in the semi-finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:33.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won the finals by default because my opponent was hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:38.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke your promise, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:41.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
